(3) 'repeatatleast' -> takes an expression and a number to be repeated a given number of times. (4) 'optional' -> takes an expression that may or may not be present. (5) 'repeat' -> repeat an expression an exact number of times. There may also be terms to denote the patterns like (1) '<cap>' -> Captial Alphabets (2) 'let' -> Both upper case and lower case letters. (3) '<num>' -> denotes a digit. (4) '<low>' -> denotes the lower case letters. (5) '<any>' -> denotes any character including numbers, letters and special characters.
